channel.title: SourceForge.net: Project File Releases: NXTCamView
channel.description: SF.net File Releases: NXTCamView (nxtcamview project) - NXTCamView is a Windows app that configures and controls the NXTCam camera sensor for Lego NXT. NXTCam (by mindsensors.com) provides real-time vision recognition to NXT robots. NXTCam is based on AVRCam and AVRCamView by John Orlando and Brent Taylor.
